query:
SELECT
                cl.source_content_id,
                cl.target_url,
                COUNT(lc.id)::integer as "click_count!"
            FROM campaign_links cl
            LEFT JOIN link_clicks lc ON cl.id = lc.link_id
            WHERE cl.source_content_id = $1
            GROUP BY cl.source_content_id, cl.target_url
            ORDER BY 3 DESC
